div1.p:
I live in Ram-alley, Gingerbread court, Bishopsgate-court


                  ; on going into my father's room (he is a shoemaker
                  ) on the 3d of August, about four o'clock in the afternoon, I saw this man with a pair of breeches in his hand, and as on as he saw me he chucked them into the box; he came out into the middle of the room, and I took him by the collar, and called for assistance; my brother came, and I delivered him up to my brother.
